This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. Additionally, the use of neural machine translation models and statistical machine translation models further supports this categorization. The paper also involves the use of word embeddings, which falls under the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of machine learning techniques such as neural networks and statistical models also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques such as post-editing, which could place it under the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
